{"tid":53780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[失蹤人口]留英港生失蹤三個月　父母赴當地尋子無果","createTime":"2016-12-25T03:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T06:45:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b24cf0babe492425e54c228afd29f869c398fdf2","tid":53780,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161224/s00001/1482556753115SL4_36EA394794C8FAD3D56EC8C08CBE00BD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161224%2Fs00001%2F1482556753115SL4_36EA394794C8FAD3D56EC8C08CBE00BD.jpg&h=9afe2840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港一名在英國南安普敦大學留學的男生失蹤近3個月，其香港家人已向當地警方報案，當地警方呼籲見過事主的人提供消息。<br />\n<br />\n20歲的康志聰(Chi Chung Hong)，英文名為「Ivan」，高約5呎6吋、中等身材、黑短髮及戴黑色眼鏡，他曾在北安普頓就讀了3年及報考A-Level，現就讀南安普敦大學(University of Southampton)生物科學系二年級。Ivan自從今年9月25日從香港返回英國，繼續其第二年學業後，只與家人聯絡了數次，最後一次通話是在10月4日。而父母給Ivan的信用卡最後使用時間為10月12日，Ivan亦沒有參加生物科學系在10月的一次考試，相信他本學期根本沒有上過課。<br />\n<br />\nIvan的父母到了當地尋找兒子，其父Eric向當地傳媒表示，他們非常擔心，因為Ivan只有二十歲，一個人身處外地。他指Ivan個性安靜及喜愛閱讀。他又說現在只想兒子盡快致電回家，只要能接觸到他，一切都可以處理得到。在香港警隊任職的Ivan母親Ida則說，兒子經常說很忙，所以他們只會每周聯絡他一次，了解他的讀書情況。<br />\n<br />\nIvan父母飛往英國尋人，又製作尋人告示，但仍沒有消息，他們將會在今日聖誕節回港，他們呼籲有Ivan消息者聯絡當地的修咸頓華人協會提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n修咸頓華人協會今午回應《明報》記者查詢時表示，目前仍未有Ivan消息，而當地警方則暫時未回應查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.singpao.com.hk/image_upload/1482605057.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Fimage_upload%2F1482605057.jpg&h=28a1c59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIvan於香港的父母親自飛往當地尋子但仍沒有消息，他們將會在今日聖誕節回港"},{"pid":"f36bb968b9bfe7568402cfc423eec4b42340fbf0","tid":53780,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6213aa9273d2f0dc3e7a5b470fba1558bf89d032","tid":53780,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"殘體字既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236cd0d6d2fba59a397498e4229fb6f003d7db3c","tid":53780,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該俾鬼佬捉左去禁室培育"},{"pid":"3ffd9a6ba1609e206884f4c656f83107c2d5da48","tid":53780,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:45:54.000Z","msg":"廿歲似四十歲<br />\n人生已完"},{"pid":"1d483631037ce5cbf39f309546beb2d664d5c613","tid":53780,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"呀叔咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de430e4c84f7481a26a8ef2de943d6e4edb6a33d","tid":53780,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殘體字既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰邊大陸仔多d咪用殘體<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊計較得咁多"},{"pid":"ab08f002a80fda935a360f7ab1f0847a6a1be328","tid":53780,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"香港警隊任職的Ivan母親Ida則說，兒子經常說很忙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完。"},{"pid":"a79b4122da35498aacb9412cdb022d9b00fc7832","tid":53780,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:12:14.000Z","msg":"報應咁快到...真係慘"},{"pid":"b60548a60514f81a894c01b45b111b95642bf514","tid":53780,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港警隊任職的Ivan母親Ida則說，兒子經常說很忙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMadam死全家唔使你教"},{"pid":"54c844345005202990b5f409c0ec6c6badd8